data.description: ****Price Improvement! Excellent price!!   Look no further! Super cute house, very well maintained. This spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath home has the comfort of a large kitchen with a cozy family room prefect for gatherings or Monday night football.  There is a beautiful dining room and formal living room to complete the ambience of this lovely home.  The backyard has new fencing to secure your dog and garden boxes ready to plant in the spring.  Updates include: New laminate flooring  throughout the home, new interior paint,  new kitchen backsplash, newer appliances.  The leased Solar by Tesla adds the luxury of lower energy bills as well as year round temperature comfort.  This home is not one to be missed. Make your appointment asap to see!
